devdoc.author: Your Name
devdoc.details: Implements time-based rounds, secure ETH handling with CEI pattern, and pseudo-random winner selection

buyTicket().details: Players can buy multiple tickets by sending exact multiples of TICKET_PRICE      Each ticket gives the player one entry in the draw

constructor.details: Sets the deployer as the owner and initializes round number to 0

returns._0: uint Number of tickets owned by the address
address[] Array of all player addresses (with duplicates for multiple tickets)
uint Total ETH in the contract
uint Seconds remaining, or 0 if no active round
bool True if a round is currently active

selectWinner().details: Can be called by anyone after the round ends      Uses pseudo-random number generation (suitable for low-stakes lottery)      Follows Checks-Effects-Interactions pattern for security

startNewRound().details: Only owner can call. Clears previous round data and sets new end time

players.details: Players can appear multiple times if they bought multiple tickets
